{"tid":184251,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"夾組最慘唔係遇到Free rider","createTime":"2017-04-02T16:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T01:23:45.000Z","uid":35581,"like":51,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5dc92712a09d9e206800e8c18eb3f3b76919f3a","tid":184251,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"唉 以前以為做Project遇到Free rider好慘啦<br />\n屌 點知唔係 <br />\n&quot;被迫Free-ride&quot;先最慘<br />\n辛辛苦苦打晒自己負責果Part 無啦啦講都唔講聲 比人改晒<br />\n原本果篇落晒Reference 全部都係Peer-reviewed journal, 又Update<br />\n至少都做左成個星期 絕對唔Hea貨<br />\n個個人Standards都唔同 你覺得唔好咪講下想點改囉<br />\n無問過我改都算 仲要周圍唱<br />\n唉 本身人緣已經差 無乜朋友 以後唔洗揾人夾組啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5129da9ddf13b09d684b540fa1e48dca4a1452","tid":184251,"uid":89953,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"邊條仆街發明group project呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係幾friend嘅人一齊做GP都會出事"},{"pid":"6c0ef7e9fda1bd00a7daef9245ecc0794c933105","tid":184251,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊條仆街發明group project呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係幾friend嘅人一齊做GP都會出事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c7b9395185ba961026e1353d196f8842083c6d","tid":184251,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"以為自己好勁要做leader 跟住係咁點人。自己又唔做 最後話你free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4b5bb1f2ef279ebcaefe352a3086b7aec49750","tid":184251,"uid":36642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲朋友係一班人，做GP係另一班人。<br />\n<br />\n幾frd都好，如果係唔夾嘅話，一齊做GP等於絕交。<br />\n<br />\n讀U果時聽講過，男女朋友唔同GP做project，女方俾人唱Free-ride。<br />\n<br />\n個男嘅同女方即時分手。CLS！"},{"pid":"af7b2aadc8301bbaf9adab5e65f9379ef2ebec2a","tid":184251,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"屌 本來夾果個都唔係我朋友黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友都算啦 有乜事叫佢直接屌就算<br />\n唔識既先慘 比人唱通街<br />\n<br />\n仲要讀多3年 都唔知點捱<br />\nBtw,我有試過叫Prof.比我SoloQ做Project<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17892422ad44f0ca1059b8156cd7075b7095e639","tid":184251,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為自己好勁要做leader 跟住係咁點人。自己又唔做 最後話你free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己有做 仲改晒全份Project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依下先慘 好似搞到我交垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老實實 佢改完又唔覺好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba1ff21956d151ce46012442c0f1174dfb1ce72","tid":184251,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:29:45.000Z","msg":"屌返佢轉頭囉<br />\n<br />\n我做嘅野唔可以俾人改"},{"pid":"f3d9caa7b04b0cf28a9693db7a231de82cddccdf","tid":184251,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁如果人地改完份野靚grade又得唔得"},{"pid":"054fa56935c9c09c16bac2651232ca8d850653be","tid":184251,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌返佢轉頭囉<br />\n<br />\n我做嘅野唔可以俾人改</blockquote><br />\n佢大把fd 得罪唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93070903610463c8ab8d7644712ee6a6859a7747","tid":184251,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果人地改完份野靚grade又得唔得</blockquote><br />\n佢改完靚Grade 都唔代表我原本果份差過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有改之前問下人好難?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c885f76c121e5d6aee2735b4947c8bde98e7b06","tid":184251,"uid":41152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為自己好勁要做leader 跟住係咁點人。自己又唔做 最後話你free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己有做 仲改晒全份Project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依下先慘 好似搞到我交垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老實實 佢改完又唔覺好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有啲仆街冚家剷鍾意人改你少少野就當自己做左野，之後問你做咩唔做野+唱你free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者係明明唔係自己做又要爭住啲重要既part去present，最尾講到成pat屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遇著呢班撚屌仲撚想死"},{"pid":"801ee78ad4d353e94485846a3d7b2373756b1d13","tid":184251,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌返佢轉頭囉<br />\n<br />\n我做嘅野唔可以俾人改</blockquote><br />\n佢大把fd 得罪唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多fd還多fd<br />\n<br />\n原則係唔可以變<br />\n<br />\n你係覺得佢錯就大條道理屌佢"},{"pid":"e16c81c8ce640071d9b0c000e9afb3ea15ab47ce","tid":184251,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁如果人地改完份野靚grade又得唔得</blockquote><br />\n佢改完靚Grade 都唔代表我原本果份差過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有改之前問下人好難?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你應該你遇到啲無料扮四條既人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae55b073e3a620f4cecf7ed584f6b17136c95de","tid":184251,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"做project 淨係想有人幫我改grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f065722aa89fd92b88e37157ba927ac8a69d1d","tid":184251,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:51:42.000Z","msg":"果條友勁開既話又無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419b90d4cf1f90cc9873a1bcde6de39589a82810","tid":184251,"uid":43171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做project 淨係想有人幫我改grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你自己唔學好grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老馮幫你改架？要人改就自己俾錢搵technical writer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa6241ee46c841d52a1c654f154f787ca72a996","tid":184251,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"試過 不過我係出到去present果時比人cut左我個part，野都冇講過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7670e65f3b2f2095ba30702d8a977456481a21db","tid":184251,"uid":68314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"根本有好多人都只係適合做朋友而唔適合一齊合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為份group project都對幾個人有不滿，如果就咁相處應該就冇事"},{"pid":"70c70bef52f13d68a9bf3b811069650aff39c85f","tid":184251,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過 不過我係出到去present果時比人cut左我個part，野都冇講過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後我話咁講唔全面，得返少少時間佢叫我自由發揮，返位屌我hea講<img src