<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班Lecturer 唔想改咁多份assignment 囉</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申最撚憎做Group project <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係個個夾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGroup 乜撚野project <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40453f70677314065df6111c5804e1f6dcaf2657","tid":184251,"uid":84954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"被freeride好慘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年讀master都試過<br />\n要三個人一gp, 仲要幫你gp左, 諗住死撚硬<br />\n點知一問兩個gp-mate, 一個讀phd take master科, 以前已經take過啲topic<br />\n另一個double-degree, 一樣take過<br />\n佢兩個一野將個project切開兩半, 一人一半去做<br />\n叫我自己搞intro+opening background+conclusion (當時心諗:con條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你兩個一人一半左&hellip;)<br />\n結果 present前兩個鐘佢2個俾野我執ppt, 連問問題打手佢兩個都準備埋<br />\n咁就A撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係present前好撚驚,真係手頭上一啲野都無<br />\n佢兩個飛機既我就真係仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d52cac156a8d4f4c5c04c6d4ef0d1a4e8ebf53","tid":184251,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"冇料扮四條又要做leader<br />\n明明方向錯/啲point on9又覺得自已啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種負戰力嘅人先最惡頂<br />\nfreerider都只係0戰力"},{"pid":"5f3b5d2b42cef4bfb98fea50c52fb2d237f12264","tid":184251,"uid":10612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦 班垃圾gpa 3都唔撚過 點信佢地阿"},{"pid":"79763d4b69ee3ecf0c002f5394ed4fe6a93d46a8","tid":184251,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"你同人地standard唔同做咩仲要同佢地一組?"},{"pid":"4c74752de10960de2326d41df72d61b7af96bbd3","tid":184251,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"撞到半free rider仲慘<br />\n臨交前一晚<br />\n交份copy既垃圾比你<br />\n迫你通頂重做<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4589480a2d41d7163c439bca338a980e1e9a040a","tid":184251,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"最後三日先蒲頭問有咩做<br />\n點撚俾你做啊 <br />\n<br />\n幫你做埋又話逼你freeride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47495f5609bb884f6ab9f6b2ea815c56803c7fd1","tid":184251,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同人地standard唔同做咩仲要同佢地一組?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1 可以係assigned<br />\n2 唔係咁易yo到同standard嘅人"},{"pid":"908cf0e2ee1cc84062717a7c4aa823a2cc36b446","tid":184251,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞到半free rider仲慘<br />\n臨交前一晚<br />\n交份copy既垃圾比你<br />\n迫你通頂重做<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndeadline fighter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e963ca9cea92408d97084ea56b7b337a3ca485c","tid":184251,"uid":38030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"題外話 幾個人夾埋寫一篇文果類gp先on9 一黎文意唔貫通 二黎每個人都有唔同文肇風格 作到出黎一定奇奇怪怪 但d on9 lecturer又成日叫人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c68e65bbbf2833fa90d22071908a2d17d2b3322","tid":184251,"uid":82874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"樓主絲定巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有個同學又係你咁嘅case"},{"pid":"4ae94376a5fdefe77405570903b1de5de72c78ab","tid":184251,"uid":4665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜有份report + present<br />\n咁其實就week 5 已經briefing 咗，week 9 present<br />\n咁week 7 果陣就約出黎傾啦 <br />\n出黎果陣果條友又好似好信得過咁 <br />\n又私底下whatsapp 我 問下呢樣得唔得 果樣得唔得<br />\n點撚知去到present 前幾日 諗住combine 埋咁多個slide 啦 一睇佢份野 100%照抄source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係已經就黎present, 唯有我同個fd 重新做過佢果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩最後A 咗"},{"pid":"74c8e23e2b383df0b6b3c44203a08c77bff22fa6","tid":184251,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話 幾個人夾埋寫一篇文果類gp先on9 一黎文意唔貫通 二黎每個人都有唔同文肇風格 作到出黎一定奇奇怪怪 但d on9 lecturer又成日叫人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成組分工做完之後最後要英文最好果個執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f677dcdc43f8a45495e5d1001be8f3a91c878e","tid":184251,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇諗過如果唔被free ride你 佢地會爛gpa? 咁樣唔怪得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229f4e2506c05a43143a30af4001620fecef4091","tid":184251,"uid":31359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我試過將人地成part del走，一條友執曬成萬字既文。<br />\n<br />\n見到d亂黎既作品，我直頭講都費時，講完去改咪又係做份差唔多出黎。<br />\n<br />\n最後份project拎A。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<br />\n最尾peer evaluation form仲要照比高分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇計。佢地係有做，只係過唔到我果關</blockquote><br />\n你呢種冇問題，至少認同人地做過野，但del/改完當你冇做過，真係死全家先"},{"pid":"f8768f1213a345c887af6bd89a40495ea138be2c","tid":184251,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"樓主本身成積好唔好，本身成績唔好比人改野係好正常"},{"pid":"bdf43602a335e9643be9ba296380e304c0f4a535","tid":184251,"uid":9975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"你諗下自已做成點先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲串串共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗唔洗我放你份野上黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe659ff461ec416d91998516009d0c7e7bb7cfe","tid":184251,"uid":79464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"曾經遇到個係 叫佢快啲做好佢個part 仲要搵資料<br />\n佢用a4紙手寫資料俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57e973ed4d95e208ecbcce657ff050ce51414b2","tid":184251,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"試過有個free rider傾野又有出現 平時講野又有文有路 臨交之前一個禮拜就開始拖 最後幾日直頭人間蒸發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d23c31aaaf1b65b16aa224b6529bebd660eb337","tid":184251,"uid":70400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗下自已做成點先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲串串共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗唔洗我放你份野上黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n組員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3876b65d6853039dd3a377ad39a92c2ca4839db1","tid":184251,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後三日先蒲頭問有咩做<br />\n點撚俾你做啊 <br />\n<br />\n幫你做埋又話逼你freeride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有四日要present 問我份pj點啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌我話唔洗啦你自己做過份交啦<br />\n即時發爛咋話自己又唔係唔做野 <br />\n我自己做哂就話佢free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗有心做會唔會而家先黎問"},{"pid":"46ea2f60d1e417f772fb65e319f865d8f0e5bbcc","tid":184251,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"有時好開心遇到咁既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問自己英文唔算好 但諗到point<br />\nLeader就相反 英文好好但point就唔夠清晰<br />\n所以佢會拾走我d point再整合<br />\n<br />\nGroup project依d真係人夾人 無得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623d37f32862cecfdeb8f90e10ab503c4eda101b","tid":184251,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊條仆街發明group project呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係幾friend嘅人一齊做GP都會出事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你岩，呢排開始發現同親某個fd做gp project就會出事，發現佢次次做project分工都未傾佢就自己做晒最簡單個part再叫其他人做，就算分左都會做埋人地個part(人地個part易d)，搞到人地都唔知點做，總之越黎越唔中意佢，已經冇以前咁fd☹️"},{"pid":"8db3966449be34e4c447a1f0e9c203c6a072344c","tid":184251,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"一直都係分開咁做<br />\n自己做自己果part, 最多幫佢改grammar同比idea<br />\n有人free-ride就等肥，peer reviewed煮死佢"},{"pid":"74439b81bb9a3da4776381c984527f28416c809c","tid":184251,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"最撚憎做pj <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但我係因為做pj而識到一班朋友 跟住一齊做左兩年pj了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc2f9f701bfbf23ab02dc974d22ad861ab9e64","tid":184251,"uid":96151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"點睇一開始就分哂 d Hea part比我做 <br />\n做好哂一直online睇下有無野可以幫手（本身已經分得少）<br />\n到第朝一起身比佢改撚哂連sub title都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102c8c98b28cf141e2694044924c35f30139fed4","tid":184251,"uid":77705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"遇到同你差唔多既情況<br />\n不過係個groupmate交垃圾俾我，最後幫佢寫過晒<br />\n本身已經忙到仆街，你估我唔想叫佢自己改<br />\n但係睇過佢原本交過黎份野，就會知叫佢改完都唔會好得幾多<br />\nbtw, 個人覺得呢種人仲仆街過freerider"},{"pid":"ee4bdca3b352195f4790beee60bbb44e7da9a2c6","tid":184251,"uid":38369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"一句講曬group project 垃撚圾 無啦啦分咩組做咩project啊 自己做自己個份咪算 最後份group project 又要分工 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fc714f4e97479c8dd13693eef58879aa14a012","tid":184251,"uid":76447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"自己做果part有幾板slide 之後俾人改 又俾人講曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住先發現原來組有隱藏free fider 成個project淨係做左一板slide仲要我做果part佢講曬 結果我自己要走去分人地part講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9d6b4e3b255ad299139a3b3b6829694b738e73","tid":184251,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"呢個禮拜要交essay，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又做咁既野比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜鬼野intro都寫到咁又唔好意思話佢做既一d可取之處都沒有。<br />\n放心一切在我掌握之中！已經準備好呢幾日通頂都做埋佢地個份：delete all --&gt; copy 自己做既 --&gt; paste<br />\nA grade當禮物送比佢地，唔好再見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1dc121602aeb96d8aa0027a9ec5407a2c423c0","tid":184251,"uid":34764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮撚晒leader果下最黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁無人做帶頭傾project分配工作 無人做第一個係大方向比意見既人 個個唔出聲等deadline先黎驚 問人點算?<br />\n我上個sem有個project有個gp mate一早分哂工 set哂internal deadline 不知做得幾順利 我又唔鍾意做deadline fighter 一早做好個心好安定 寧願有個獨裁leader 都唔想個個都驚蝕底驚責任要等其他組員出聲"}]}